This code attempts to automate all of the calculations required for the design of a generic spark gap Tesla coil.

TeslaStats calculates the parameters for all of the components of a spark gap Tesla coil.
This includes information about the Neon Sign Transformer (NST), Primary Tank Capacitor (PTC), Primary Coil (PRI), Secondary Coil (SEC), and Topload (TOP).

MMCCalc calcuates overall voltage and capacitance ratings of a Multiple Mini Capacitor (MMC) Bank.
